text: The Federal Parliament of Nepal (संघीय संसद नेपाल, Saṅghīya Sansada Nēpāla) is the bicameral federal and supreme legislature of Nepal. It was established in 2018. It has the National Assembly and the House of Representatives as parallel houses. ==References== Category:Government of Nepal Category:Organizations based in Nepal Nepal Nepal Nepal Category:2018 establishments in Asia
title: Federal Parliament of Nepal
